\log(1-k)
\begin{align} 1 - (1-k)^n \ge& S\\ 1 - S \ge& (1-k)^n\\ \log(1-S) \ge& \log\left[(1-k)^n\right]\\ \log(1-S) \ge& n\log(1-k)\\ \frac{\log(1-S)}{\log(1-k)} \le& n\\ n \ge& \frac{\log(1-S)}{\log(1-k)} \end{align}
